cs.LG, cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.NE 

This paper deals with neural network scoring functions and their use in structured prediction tasks, which are common in natural language processing and computer vision. Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.CL (Computation and Language), and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, since the paper specifically focuses on sequence labeling datasets, cs.CV (Computer Vision) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) are also possible sub-categories.
